Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Intro}Intro
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.98,0:01:28.98,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{OP}OP
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:02:59.03,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Part A}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:49.10,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Part B}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.06,0:21:38.06,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{ED}ED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.03,0:23:08.03,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Outro}Outro
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.58,0:00:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, can I say something amazing right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,As for how amazing it is-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.91,0:00:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.10,0:00:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and say it. Chop-chop.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, embarking on that "first step"\Ntakes courage, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.42,0:00:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The... Dharma... Doll...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.76,0:00:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Fell down. Like when you play that game?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.27,0:00:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm talking about something on\Na much larger scale!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.27,0:00:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,For example...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.07,0:00:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The human race that first ate natto must've had\Nsome ridiculous amount of courage, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.50,0:00:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That stuff's practically rotten beans, you know.\NNormally, would you even think of eating it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.18,0:00:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The first person who ate durian\Nmust've been crazy too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.31,0:00:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, someone like Kusaya!\NI mean, her name's Kusaya for crying out loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.26,0:00:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She's like beyond imposing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.95,0:00:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Put it on top of piping hot rice! Skip the hot mustard!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.76,0:00:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,More! More of the smell!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.60,0:00:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{Missing Line}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.45,0:00:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It's irresistible! This stench!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.52,0:00:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Long live Princess Kusaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.39,0:00:49.65,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Hooray! Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.39,0:00:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,With that being said, I have decided\Nto embark on my first step too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.91,0:00:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Tanaka, will at this time, gather up my courage and...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.03,0:00:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll eat a loaf of bread that's\Nthree years past its expiration date!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.66,0:00:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.28,0:00:59.58,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Go right ahead and eat it!\NAnd then get an upset stomach!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.58,0:01:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite the mold. It's like a forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.34,0:01:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing! Isn't it amazing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.69,0:01:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.65,0:01:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.49,0:01:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.64,0:03:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Please excuse me for calling out to you so suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Based on uniform and ribbon colors,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.85,0:03:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized that you're 1st-years at Saijo,\Nso I couldn't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.68,0:03:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well that's fine, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, do you know of a person named Hisui Kujyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kujyo...? I've heard of that name before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe she's in the same class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm her younger twin sister, and my name is Kohaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, this is a rather intrusive request but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you become friends with my big sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, my big sister tends to\Nrefuse to go to school and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, I haven't seen her much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we entered school, I can probably\Ncount on my fingers how often she's shown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}At this rate, she won't meet the number of attendance \Ndays required, and she'll probably be expelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's why you're asking us to be friends with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.43,0:03:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,My big sister has been a little different since childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanta-kun, what should we play today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:48.83,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Hamburgers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:50.41,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Not what you wanna eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:53.17,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Jeez Wanta-kun, you're such a pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with picture books and TV programs,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.93,0:03:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,rather than the heartful stories\Nthat normal kids delight in...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.56,0:04:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}She was the kid that preferred the kind of grotesque \Nones where blood would spray out everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And then she grew up just the same way,\Nand rather than real living human beings,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.91,0:04:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,my big sister took an interest in\Nzombies and occult stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.93,0:04:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Gradually, she ended up\Nspooking everyone around her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.31,0:04:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My big sister isn’t good at communicating for herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.36,0:04:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and even when asked why she's\Nnot inclined to head to school...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She'd only say, "because I don't have friends"\Nor "because it's boring" or stuff like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.89,0:04:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I remember! It's Majo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Majo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.53,0:04:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the nickname I gave to Hisui Kujyo awhile back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Well, that fits my big sister perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.83,0:04:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we're totally fine with being her friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.51,0:04:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.99,0:04:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Uh, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.95,0:04:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you sure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Never hesitate to do what's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gone ahead and summoned\Nmy big sister here right away...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.48,0:04:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Younger sister, you sure act fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.03,0:04:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike the older sister, the younger sister\Nis rather aggressive, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... That's why I feel responsible and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.86,0:04:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,When we were born,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.11,0:05:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I took away all of my big sister's\Ncommunication abilities and normal sensibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It was said that maybe my big sister\Nwas left with only remnant trash...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Those were some terrible things\Nthat were said to you, Big Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What's left is for my big sister to come-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.34,0:05:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.73,0:05:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis, that was fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.43,0:05:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Way too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis, they're people from the same class as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.91,0:05:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you tricked me, Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I came as fast as I could, because you said\Nthat you'd found a bipedal tsuchinoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You came here, seriously believing that?!\NYou've got a pure heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello there. I'm the bipedal walking tsuchinoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.78,0:05:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna complicate things, so you shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.39,0:05:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Hey wait! Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.67,0:05:45.81,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Lemme go! I'm going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.81,0:05:48.74,Alternate,,0,0,0,,I'm going home! Lemme go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.63,0:05:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure you wanna go home?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.38,0:05:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when everyone has kindly said\Nthat they'll be your friend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,R-really...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.08,0:05:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, it's for real!\NLet's go tsuchinoko searching together!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you gotta come to school starting tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,P-please let me think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Or so she said yesterday, but...\NIs she gonna come? That Majo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.13,0:06:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! If she doesn't come,\Nthen I'll use this thing I took at the river recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.35,0:06:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll summon her with this photo of Tamassie,\Nthe unidentified mysterious animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.63,0:06:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, if you're gonna take a trick photo,\Nthen put a little more effort into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, she came!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.81,0:06:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Majo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Here! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.51,0:06:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,G-good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.46,0:06:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,H-hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,U-um... This is a thank you for\Nhaving made your acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.73,0:06:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I pulled an all-nighter and made these last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.23,0:06:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A friendship bracelet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.18,0:06:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I put in a wish that you would be\Nfriendly to me forever and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I put my heart and soul into braiding them...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.33,0:06:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.71,0:06:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Or rather, this material is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.52,0:06:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,B-by any chance, is this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.38,0:07:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my hair but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.97,0:07:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's freaky!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.98,0:07:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it called? That yummy thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That thing where a cut is made around the belly\Nand then stuffed with rice and stewed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.97,0:07:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-when you say a cut is made in\Nthe abdomen and rice put in and it's stewed...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about torture?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to get your hopes up,\Nbut she's talking about cooking, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,C-cooking?! M-my apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.92,0:07:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you were talking about human-eaters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You just have to link things directly to that stuff, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.25,0:07:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Aiight! I'll take on whatever you dish out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.27,0:07:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember now! It's samgyetang!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Samgyetang!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Aw... I'm kinda getting hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.90,0:07:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Well, I do have salicylic acid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.33,0:07:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What's that? Is it tasty?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}If you drink it straight up, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.44,0:07:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Um... That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.62,0:07:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't able to join the conversations at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot! 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.38,0:07:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot what Kohaku had told me yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.75,0:07:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Noooooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.54,0:07:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for friendship bracelets for\NBaka-san and the others...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.45,0:08:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez! Big Sis, why did you have to go\Nand be so you, Big Sis?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want your friends to dislike you,\Nthen you can't talk one-sidedly about the occult.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.63,0:08:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,B-but... Then, what do I talk about...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.48,0:08:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"Right!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"Funny!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,"Cute!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.33,0:08:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}If you reuse these three for different occasions, then for \Nthe time being, you'll be able to converse with high school girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.31,0:08:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"Right." "Funny." "Cute."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.75,0:08:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.35,0:08:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you! I haven't seen you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I got suddenly talked to!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,State your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.38,0:08:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,R...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.68,0:08:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So, her name is "Right."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.76,0:08:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you, why haven't you come to school more often?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.41,0:08:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of attribute are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,F...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.32,0:08:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Funny...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.92,0:08:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.00,0:08:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't know, then I'll tell you, but you\Nshouldn't joke around too much towards me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.21,0:09:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite how I look, I am the chosen one\Nwith the hidden power of the dragon, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,As it were, I am a presence to be feared!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.36,0:09:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She's totally messing with me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.64,0:09:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you bastard! There'll probably come a time\Nwhen we'll fight each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.91,0:09:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,F-fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been disliked without warning...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.72,0:09:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna eat kalbi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.05,0:09:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I do have carbinoxamine maleate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it tasty?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.15,0:09:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop checking every single time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.26,0:09:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's most important, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.70,0:09:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine if you mix it in with the barbeque sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.35,0:09:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Why Kujyo, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.81,0:09:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good you came to school. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.58,0:09:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei is happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Paranormal photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.55,0:09:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Kujyo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I went and gathered all the printouts\Nthat were passed out while you were absent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the materials from\Nworld history, and these-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.21,0:09:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,R-right thats...
Comment: 0,0:09:56.65,0:09:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Comment: 0,0:09:57.76,0:10:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Am I interpreting it correctly with "right that" \Nas the demonstrative pronouns, and "s" as the ending suffix?
Comment: 0,0:10:01.04,0:10:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is it an acronym?
Comment: 0,0:10:02.02,0:10:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she taking the first letters of Reimen,\NThe napolitan, and Somen noodles,
Comment: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,to make "Right ThatS"...?
Comment: 0,0:10:05.41,0:10:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:10:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2\move(4478.667,999,-2596.666,999,29,9747)}What does that mean? Am I interpreting it correctly with "right that" as the demonstrative pronouns, and "s" as the ending suffix? Or is it an acronym? Is she taking the first letters of Reimen, The napolitan, and Somen noodles, to make "Right ThatS"...? I don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.89,0:10:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.40,0:10:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.47,0:10:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't talk at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.13,0:10:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Loli!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I already told you, I'm not getting on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.31,0:10:24.46,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Come on, don't be afraid. Don't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.46,0:10:25.15,Alternate,,0,0,0,,I'll bite ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.15,0:10:26.50,Alternate,,0,0,0,,It's okay if you bite me, just get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.50,0:10:27.20,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Enough! I'm going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.20,0:10:28.37,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Before you go home, get on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:29.27,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Gimme a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.12,0:10:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's absolutely impossible for me to have that kind of friendly conversation...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm not cut out for school after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.78,0:10:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Majo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's head home together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We take the train, so it'll only be part-way, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.76,0:10:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,F... F... F... F...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.79,0:10:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! What is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.30,0:10:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! You don't have to worry about that.\NYou can say what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.65,0:10:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Like me. I open my mouth and\NI say stuff like poop, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.53,0:10:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You mend your ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.47,0:10:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.16,0:10:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,P-people... And all of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:10:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That is, I'm scared of being disliked and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.56,0:11:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I get so caught up just thinking about that and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.61,0:11:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I just totally can't do it well and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why... I shut myself away in my own little world...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's safe if I stay there...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.07,0:11:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that way, I can avoid\Nbeing disliked and getting hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.19,0:11:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.29,0:11:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But... The truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible to be liked by every single person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.09,0:11:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You should just make sure to cherish\Nthe people who do understand you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.66,0:11:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Robo-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.27,0:11:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Gah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.30,0:11:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's stop with this gloomy mood!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna make me itchy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Carbinoxamine maleate also works well on itchiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.39,0:11:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?! Kalbi does?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.45,0:11:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No! She's not talking about kalbi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.35,0:11:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,"You should just make sure to cherish\Nthe people who do understand you."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Will I be able to do it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis, let's go see a movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.40,0:12:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.22,0:12:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,D-do we really have to see something like this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.97,0:12:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's bad enough that it's a holiday\Nand there's a lot of people...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like a romance movie is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's setting the bar too high.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.47,0:12:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not high!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.03,0:12:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis, you've gotta know more\Nabout the trends of normal girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.40,0:12:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.51,0:12:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to be able to have fun conversations\Nwith your friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.77,0:12:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll go buy something to drink,\Nso wait here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.70,0:12:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,In the same class...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.98,0:12:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I believe Baka-san said...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.87,0:12:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe Tanaka said...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:49.70,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Loli-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Majo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you in the same class as Big Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.75,0:13:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.98,0:13:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{Missing Line?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.88,0:13:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Twins?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.42,0:13:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Kohaku, her younger twin sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.12,0:13:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So, are you here to see "Love with you" as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.13,0:13:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it. I mean, yes, that's so,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's not as if I came to see this movie\Nbecause I wanted to, or anything like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.40,0:13:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Loli-chan, you may be able to\Nlearn about the adult world,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.12,0:13:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,by watching stuff like romance movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.14,0:13:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,An acquaintance strongly recommended me to, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.93,0:13:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,M-me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.66,0:13:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I totally don't like these kind of chick flicks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're both so difficult!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.35,0:13:36.78,Alternate,,0,0,0,,I... I don't want Ryuji to have you after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.78,0:13:38.46,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Hey...! Where are we going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:40.79,Alternate,,0,0,0,,You've also got your girlfriend Lisa, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.12,0:13:46.25,Alternate,,0,0,0,,I can't help it, now that I've realized \Nthat the one who's really important to me, is you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.25,0:13:47.18,Alternate,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.18,0:13:50.35,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, when I saw the manganji chili pepper
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.35,0:13:52.40,Alternate,,0,0,0,,in your bento lunch box, it made me think...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.40,0:13:55.94,Alternate,,0,0,0,,That I can't lie to myself, about my feelings anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.94,0:13:58.03,Alternate,,0,0,0,,But, that was Lisa's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.03,0:14:00.01,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Do you know the manganji chili pepper's
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.01,0:14:01.01,Alternate,,0,0,0,,flower meaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.01,0:14:02.58,Alternate,,0,0,0,,I don't know something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.58,0:14:03.93,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.93,0:14:06.07,Alternate,,0,0,0,,It's "I won't let you go, for the rest of your life!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw! So cool! This makes my heart skip a beat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.56,0:13:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This man... That he's forcing a woman who has\Na significant other to go with him is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.64,0:13:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that, he has his own significant other too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.67,0:13:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,These bastards...!\NThey're skipping school like it's no big deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.36,0:13:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Their parents would cry if they ever found out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:13:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This kind of messy romance is normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.54,0:14:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans are scary after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not even going out yet,\Nbut they're holding hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.24,0:14:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They're like super delinquents...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:09.19,Alternate,,0,0,0,,No! If someone saw us like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.19,0:14:10.83,Alternate,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to, then stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.58,0:14:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw! How wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.94,0:14:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw... How boring that not a\Nsingle drop of blood is being spilt...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.12,0:14:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish someone would get killed soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.98,0:14:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A maiden who's not even married yet is k-kis...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What if a child sees something like this...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.89,0:14:13.94,Alternate,,0,0,0,,I love you, Erika...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.94,0:14:14.89,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Yuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.64,0:14:17.62,Alternate,,0,0,0,,I'll never let you go again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:20.81,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Even if the manganji chili pepper's flower dies...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.43,0:14:23.99,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.59,0:14:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That was good, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.35,0:14:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.59,0:14:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That was entertaining!\NIt was a tearjerker at the end, you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.81,0:14:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}The kind of thinking that as long as you and your own \Nare happy, then you don't care about other people is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.22,0:14:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,horrifying...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.35,0:14:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like the movie was\Njam-packed with people's egoism.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.23,0:14:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The serious main character was corrupted by\Na delinquent and steadily became irresponsible...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.82,0:14:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a movie that should've gotten a R12 rating...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.61,0:14:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you go to the movie theater by yourself a lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.75,0:14:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's like so mature!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.11,0:14:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.23,0:15:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess. There' no one of\Nthe same age that I can casually invite, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.82,0:15:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.79,0:15:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When it comes to high school girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,just inviting them might make them say\Nsomething like "die!", so it's s-scary, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I-it seems like... Maybe Loli-san understands me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:10.95,Alternate,,0,0,0,,What's with that?\NMajo, it's like you don't stand out at school,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.95,0:15:13.51,Alternate,,0,0,0,,but outside from it,\Nyou're kinda different than what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.51,0:15:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Um, Loli-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.06,0:15:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.70,0:15:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.60,0:15:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There'll be other chances to talk to her. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.51,0:15:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.33,0:15:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Baka-san, Wota-san, Robo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's up, Majo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.42,0:15:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I came up with just a little game, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.03,0:15:42.04,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.03,0:15:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a "ways of dying Amida lottery."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you pick the number you want,\Nand it'll forecast the way you'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need for you to explain it carefully. \NWe more or less have an idea of what it entails.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You've come up with another icky game again...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.13,0:15:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured you'd jump at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.05,0:15:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, number three for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.44,0:16:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Three it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.65,0:16:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... It goes here and then this way and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be "beaten to death."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.82,0:16:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Robo, you got just the right blunt weapon with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.74,0:16:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the efficient thing would be\Nthe corners of the desk or chair-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.79,0:16:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not getting killed, all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Wota, you do it next!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you can die in the most pitiful way possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.13,0:16:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's just plain old bad-mouthing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.01,0:16:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, this only has pitiful ways to die, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.27,0:16:25.42,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Target: Kujyo. Codename "Majo", spotted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.42,0:16:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though that one hardly came to school at all,\Nshe all of a sudden appeared a few days ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.45,0:16:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and before anyone noticed, she'd integrated\Nherself with Baka and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.06,0:16:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Suspicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.97,0:16:37.30,Alternate,,0,0,0,,How about adding skewered,\Nskinned alive, or the Brazen Bull?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.30,0:16:41.55,Alternate,,0,0,0,,It's where a person is put inside a hollow\Nbrass bull and fire is put under it to...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.55,0:16:43.23,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Those are all executions or torture!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.23,0:16:44.64,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Isn't it wonderful?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.64,0:16:45.96,Alternate,,0,0,0,,Gah! I'm gonna live!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.12,0:16:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Danger level three.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll continue tracking from here on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.63,0:16:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayday, mayday. Please respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of danger levels,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,what you're doing there puts you\Nat the final stage, Yamamoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.24,0:16:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Loli-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.09,0:17:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's the girl from Class 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So cute. She looks like an elementary student.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me, you airheads!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.79,0:17:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get cleaning!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.54,0:17:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's go. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.53,0:17:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't able to talk to her again today...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.63,0:17:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You should just make sure to cherish\Nthe people who do understand you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.88,0:17:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be too difficult after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.12,0:17:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Hey you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.37,0:17:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.10,0:17:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe you're... Yamai-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.76,0:17:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just an alias, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Majo, or whatever your name is.\NYou're hiding something, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.78,0:17:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You may have been able to deceive the others,\Nbut it won't work on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay... Yamai-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Just tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.97,0:17:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.47,0:17:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You know... I can see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.52,0:17:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,your underwear...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.74,0:17:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.89,0:17:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.20,0:17:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.33,0:17:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I-I was showing it on purpose,\Nto throw you off guard, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.89,0:18:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.42,0:18:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,H-h-how's that?! You got thrown off guard, right?!\NAnd it got you rattled, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.73,0:18:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all according to plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.66,0:18:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You better not tell anyone\Nwhat you just saw. You got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.21,0:18:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.74,0:18:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,M-m-more importantly,\Nhurry up and give up your secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! E-even if you say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.76,0:18:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Secret... Secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.15,0:18:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.04,0:18:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better if you don't tell normal people\Nthat you like this kind of stuff, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.29,0:18:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I like seeing people's blood,\Nmore than anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.17,0:18:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.94,0:18:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}E-Especially, I can't get enough of the sight of blood, \Nvigorously gushing out from the carotid artery...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.17,0:18:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and of course, I also love when the\Ninternal organs pulsate after being dragged out...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.10,0:18:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.75,0:18:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...far more than I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Like serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you two over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.44,0:18:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got something to do, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.31,0:18:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you take care of the rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.01,0:18:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.21,0:19:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the hell do we have to do\Nyour share of things...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.22,0:19:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, um... I've got this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.87,0:19:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll deal with their cleanup altogether, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.49,0:19:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.50,0:19:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She's gonna clean both of them up altogether?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.10,0:19:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Cleanup done...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.87,0:19:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you guys, hurry up and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.83,0:19:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.23,0:19:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! There's no need to go that far, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.78,0:19:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to do it by yourself, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.63,0:19:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\t(0,600,\alpha&H00&)\t(600,1200,\alpha&HFF&)\t(1200,1800,\alpha&H00&)\t(1800,2400,\alpha&HFF&)}You know... You know... You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.14,0:19:22.89,Alternate,,0,0,0,,So kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.48,0:19:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, then since things are more or less done, shall \Nwe also just finish up by throwing out the trash?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.89,0:19:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yeah, sure! Let's do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.49,0:19:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll go get the dustpan, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.67,0:19:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You dropped some...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.50,0:19:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.47,0:19:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamai-san! Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I already took care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.75,0:19:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The trash?! With your bare hands?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.13,0:19:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll throw out the trash too,\Nso you go ahead and head home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.03,0:19:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What? B-but...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.52,0:20:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I-it's fine. It's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.43,0:20:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,When it comes to Majo...\NWhen it comes to Majo, I must not piss her off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.30,0:20:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't get to say thank you to Yamai-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.81,0:20:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,but she sure is a good person...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.87,0:20:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Majo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been waiting for ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.53,0:20:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job with the cleaning duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.47,0:20:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Loli!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.88,0:20:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry, so let's eat something!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.40,0:20:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Loli-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.31,0:20:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Majo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.91,0:20:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The Choco-bat's yummy, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.94,0:20:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.94,0:20:35.17,Alternate,,0,0,0,,I-I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.38,0:20:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Loli-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,U-um... n-next time... t-together... a-a-a movie...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.68,0:20:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to go see one...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and the next one will be like a heartwarming \Nstory with no delinquents showing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.24,0:20:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I'm sorry! That's a no, right?\NWe haven't even gotten close yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.17,0:20:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just gonna go hang myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.77,0:20:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,0:21:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You better invite me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.91,0:21:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.74,0:21:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.87,0:21:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Majo's Choco Bat is a home run!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.33,0:21:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! It's true! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.74,0:21:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the first time I've seen one!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.01,0:21:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky! You're so lucky! I wanna home run too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.67,0:21:22.05,Alternate,,0,0,0,,You just keep striking out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.67,0:21:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,About today, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.84,0:21:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,will probably never forget the taste of the\NChoco Bat that I ate together with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.80,0:21:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.06,0:21:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop preserving anything\Nand everything in formalin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.68,0:21:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably for the rest of my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.08,0:23:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This kind of movie really does\Nfeel heartwarming after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.54,0:23:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Majo and Loli are probably enjoying\Nthe movie about now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.11,0:23:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? Robo, what're you drawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.65,0:23:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I've tried to make one for Baka as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.37,0:23:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A reincarnation Amida lottery.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.97,0:23:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's one of those about what you'll become\Nif you get reborn, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.11,0:23:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.80,0:23:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I pick number five!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.20,0:23:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Face mite...
